Simpsons Cartoon Studio   Description:

is a powerful animation tool kit that includes many cartoon building blocks to create your own original Simpsons cartoons. Pick a background. Choose your favorite characters. Then, add props, special effects and sounds. The Simpsons Cartoon Studio makes it easy to put everything together and bring your cartoon creations to life.
